  "description": "<i>Wizard's Gold</i> is a text adventure game for the 8-bit Atari.<br><br>The player begins their adventure within the bedroom of a wizard's house, with the goal to find a hidden bar of gold within the dark catacombs beneath his home.  The player must explore a variety of rooms, including: the broom repair room, a psychedelic room, an aquarium, and a fungus room.  <br><br>All commands are via VERB NOUN entry. The player can ask for help at any time to get advice on specific areas. There is no save or restore feature.",
